    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――鏡の前で可愛いポーズを研究中",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Studying cute poses in front of the mirror",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 4.6666668972
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、もう少し上目遣いで……\nあざとくなり過ぎず、自然な感じで……にぃーっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ummー‚ look up a little more…\nNot too tricky‚ but natural… smileー",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6666668972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 15.7999994677
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "ぬぁーっ！　ダメ……こころの可愛いポーズは\nどーしてもあざとさが強く出ちゃう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ughー! No… Kokoro's cute pose\nalways comes across as too tricky",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.7999994677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、そこがこころの良さでもあり\nこころの可愛いさでもあるんだけど～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ that's both Kokoro's strength and\nKokoro's cuteness~…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.0666644812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_tokyokkrroom-00-night",
      "startTime": 30.5666623195
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "可愛いの頂点に君臨すべく、全方位可愛いを目指す\nこころとしては自然な可愛さも手に入れたいところ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To reach the top of cuteness‚ aim for cuteness in every way\nKokoro would also wants to obtain natural cuteness…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.5666623195,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、部屋に籠もってても何も思いつかないし……\n外で新しい可愛いポーズのアイデアを探そうかな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ummー‚ can't think of anything even if I stay locked in my room…\nLet's find some new cute pose ideas outside~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4666623195,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9833.335637999993
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.7333307822
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "（あれは……すみれちゃん……？）\n（すずにゃんと何か喋ってるみたいだけど……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Is that… Sumire-chan…?）\n（It looks like she's talking to Suzu-nyan about something…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.8666579962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.7999903123
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ！？　こんなにお菓子もらっちゃっていいの？\nうわぁ、すっごく嬉しい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehe!? Is it okay if I have this snack?\nWow‚ I'm so happy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.7999903123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.9333236456
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、すずちゃん！　食べるの楽しみだなぁ\n食べたらすぐ感想送るね！　じゃあまたね～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ Suzu-chan! I'm looking forward to eating it\nI'll send you a review as soon as I try it! See you next time~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.9333236456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.5999903123
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "（すずにゃんから！？　あんなにお菓子をもらってる？）\n（万年金欠のはずの……すずにゃんから……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（To Suzu-nyan!? Did she get that many snacks?）\n（To the cheapskate… Suzu-nyan…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.5999903123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.0999903123
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんだか……強い視線を感じるような……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Something… I feel a strong gaze…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.0999903123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.0999943812
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "（はっ！？　隠れないとっ！）\n（……今度は怜ちゃんがすみれちゃんの方に……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Oh!? I need to hide!）\n…This time‚ Rei-chan goes to where Sumire-chan is…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.0999943812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.3333277146
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "え、このマカロン私にくれるんですか？\nありがとうございます！　とっても嬉しいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ are you giving me this macaron?\nThank you! I'm very happy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.3333277146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.8999943812
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "このお店いつも並んでる人気店ですよね！\n箱も可愛くて、食べるのが楽しみです～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This store is so popular that there's always a line!\nBox is so cute and I'm looking forward to eating it~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.8999943812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.6666671514
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "（自然な喜び方……自然な笑顔……自然な可愛さ……）\n（これが自然な愛され妹キャラすみれの真の力……！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Natural way to enjoy… natural smile… natural cuteness…）\n（Is this the true power of beloved little sister character sumire…!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.6666671514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.1333307663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "（あ、今度はkanaさんがすみれちゃんのところに……）\n（いやいや、まさかkanaさんが声を掛ける訳――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ah‚ this time kana-chan is where Sumire is…）\n（No-no‚ there's no way kana-chan would talk to――）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.1333307663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.2666702031
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "あっ！　kanaさん、お疲れ様です～！　この間は\nありがとうございました～！　けん玉楽しかったです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! kana-san‚ thank you for your effort~! I appreciate\nlast time~! Kendama was fun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.2666702031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.3666646242
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.9666661341
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "え、この紙袋なんですか？　けん玉を教えてくれた\nお礼……？　いやいや、あれは仕事で――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ what is this paper bag? A reward for teaching\nme Kendama…? No-no‚ that was work――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.9666661341,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-03.m4a",
          "delay": 15066.665156699997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.7666569788
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました、それじゃあ、ありがたく受け取ります！\nわぁ、可愛いリップ！　早速明日使ってみますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ then‚ I'll gratefully accept!\nWow‚ what a cute lip balm! I'll try it out tomorrow!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.3999979575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.8999979575
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.8999903122
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "（すみれちゃん……kanaさんまでも虜に？　うう……）\n（負けてられません、こころももっと精進しないと……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sumire-chan… you captured even kana-chan? Woo…）\n（I can't lose‚ Kokoro must work harder‚ too…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.8999903122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 167.933321611
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kkr_01_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "（部屋に戻ってすみれちゃんの可愛いを）\n（徹底解析じゃーいっ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Let's go back to room and thoroughly analyze）\n（Sumire's cutenessー!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.933321611,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
